        <source>addTAMaster(_taMaster : CM_TerminalAreaMaster) updating;
/*
Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
22/08/2011	cnwdap1	Initial creation PAR #28047 CCMS POL 2095
